She draws her gun and points it at Black Aracnia. "YOU"LL PAY FOR 
THIS!!"  She ran up and punched the computer screen and destroyed the 
screen.  She drew her hand back and watched the cuts and damage to 
her hand heal up.  She looked at Black Aracnia and puts her gun away.

"Now let's get out of here.  He'll think I shot you after I punched 
the screen.  Now let's go."
